\left\|x \right\| = \sum_{i=1}^{i=n}\left|x^i\right|
d\left(x\right)=\sum_{i=1}^{i=n}x^i\ln x^i
x\in R^n 
 \sum_{i=1}^{i=n}x^i=1
x, x'
\left| d\left(x\right)-d(x') \right|\leq \frac{1}{2}\left\|x-x' \right\|
\left\|x \right\| = \sum_{i=1}^{i=n}\left|x^i\right|
d\left(x\right)=\sum_{i=1}^{i=n}x^i\ln x^i
x\in \left\{R^n \mid x\ge0,\sum_{i=1}^{i=n}x^i=1\right\}
d_1\left(x\right)\ge \frac{1}{2}\left\|x-x_0\right\|
x_0= \operatorname{argmin}_x \left\{d_1\left(x\right)\right\}
x_0^i=\frac{1}{2},i=1,2,...,n
